Mr James Fraser of Fraser's Ridge.

12:17.270 --> 12:19.397
Mr Edmund Fanning,
my dear friend and colleague.

12:20.570 --> 12:23.448
A pleasure, sir. My wife, Claire Fraser.

12:24.490 --> 12:26.981
