13:35.770 --> 13:38.352
If I were to examine it,
I could know for sure.

13:39.650 --> 13:41.561
My wife is a healer, Mr Fanning.

13:41.820 --> 13:42.855
Ah...

13:43.070 --> 13:46.562
Well, let us defer
to Mr Fanning's physician, shall we?

13:47.030 --> 13:50.409
